title: I currently own all the skins in the store. How to obtain some of the others?
body:
I'm just curious on how to obtain some of these skins? I know some of them are exclusive to set ranks which can never be obtain. Wukong and Rumble skins aren't released just yet so they are there
My Main question is how does one Obtain Rusty Blizcrank? I've always thought of it as a good joke skin but you can't buy it in the store anymore ;;
